Gatara lands and kicks the Maximal once to make sure he's not 
faking.  She puts another few bullets into him for good measure, then 
scoops him up and flings him into the air, nailing him with a grenade 
while he's up for target practice.

Kenzo was badly damaged by the weaponfire.  The bullets scarred the

lock.
